# =============================================================================
# UnifiedOps v2 — Production env
#
# Copy to `frontend/.env.production` and adjust on the UI RHEL server.
# Read at `vite build` time and baked into the bundle.
#
# In production the React bundle is served by FastAPI (server.py) on
# the same origin, so /api and /ws are co-hosted — no proxy needed.
# The /influx* paths are still served by server.py as reverse proxies
# to the per-server InfluxDB endpoints on the three RHEL listener VMs.
# =============================================================================

# Empty = use same-origin /api and /ws (recommended).
# Override only if the UI is behind nginx / Caddy at a different host.
VITE_DEV_API_TARGET=
